author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Ceiling joist leveling tips…I’m using 1/4 inch cedar lath to level the joists. These are nice because they’re easy to tack in place with brad nails. Having level ceiling joists makes drywall easier to install and it’s important for shower wall tile 🔥#carpentry #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
